/AGENTS.md              @dokhiem2k4
/CONTRIBUTING.md        @dokhiem2k4

# ============================================================================
# HARNESS CORE — _context và _meta (high-risk PR area)
# Cần team lead + 1 reviewer khác
# ============================================================================
